@(78-82=c18151.78) …… addressed (?) ……: @q[Enkidu,Gilgamec]{“You who have gone to sleep, you who have gone to sleep ……! Young Lord @wRN{Gilgameš}, how long will you sleep for? The mountains are becoming indistinct as the shadows fall across them; the evening …….”}

@(83-89=c18151.83) @wRN{Gilgameš} awoke from his dream, shuddering from his sleep. He rubbed his eyes; there was eery silence everywhere. @q[Gilgamec,Enkidu]{“By the life of my own mother @wDN{Ninsumun} and of my father, holy @wDN{Lugalbanda}! My personal god @wDN{Enki}, Lord @wDN{Nudimmud} ……!
$ (2 lines missing)”}

@(90-95=c18151.90) @q[Enkidu,Gilgamec]{“I ……, he vexes (?) me -- the warrior whose face is a lion's grimace, and whose breast is like a raging flood. No one dare approach his brow, which devours the reedbeds. On his tongue, like that of a man-eating lion, the blood never dries. You do not have enough strength for the warrior, such is his might.”}

