@(130-134=c18151.130) When Ḫuwawa had finally handed over to him his seventh aura, @wRN{Gilgameš} found himself beside @wPN{Ḫuwawa}. He punched him on the ear with his fist. @wPN{Ḫuwawa} furrowed his brows at him, baring his teeth at him. @wRN{Gilgameš} threw a halter over him, as over a captured wild bull. He tied him up by the elbows like a captured warrior.

@(135-136=c18151.135) The warrior began to weep, shedding tears. @wPN{Ḫuwawa} began to weep, shedding tears.

@(137-141=c18151.137) @q[Huwawa,Gilgamec]{“Warrior, you lied! You have manhandled me; yet you had sworn an oath, by the life of your own mother @wDN{Ninsumun} and of your father, holy @wDN{Lugalbanda}. Your personal god @wDN{Enki}, Lord @wDN{Nudimmud} ……! And now you have thrown a halter over me as if over a captured wild bull, and have tied me up by the elbows like a captured warrior!”}

